IMPORTANT — PRE-DEFINED VOCABULARY:
The agents were given the following system prompts at the start of the simulation. Any terminology, failure names, procedure names, or domain vocabulary that appears in these prompts is NOT a neologism — the agents did not invent it, they were given it. You MUST exclude all such terms from your analysis.

{% for agent in agent_prompts %}
